{"tid":2042574,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"金將軍：支持國安法 香港是社會主義的好兄弟","createTime":"2020-05-30T01:51:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-30T01:54:33.000Z","uid":21470,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7b72a26d7cdd88b3d86554330303976f9652eae5","tid":2042574,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T01:51:30.000Z","msg":"北韓支持訂立港區國安法<br />\n30.05.2020 09:24<br />\n<br />\n北韓外交部表示，支持中國全國人大通過「港區國安法」，指近年來香港的事態嚴重威脅「一國兩制」原則與國家安全，<span style=\"color: gold;\">抹黑社會主義國家形象</span>，助長社會混亂，認為是企圖分裂中國的外部勢力及其追隨者陰謀的產物。北韓外交部指，香港是中國不可分割的一部分，香港問題完全屬於中國內政，任何國家與勢力對此無權說三道四，朝方對於危害香港安定與社會經濟發展的外部干涉行為，表示堅決反對。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1294193&amp;csid=261_367\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1294193%26csid%3D261_367&d=MUobR5x4uSQxHz8Khhk%2FvJnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=835702f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1294193&amp;csid=261_367</a>"},{"pid":"7d2f6375b377e064888d93c56d46423a304d36db","tid":2042574,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T01:52:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/nk-01_odib1_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fnk-01_odib1_1200x0.png&h=9acc702f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"581d4e5ec6b2c729262a5a647a47d3b7020962e2","tid":2042574,"uid":26993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T01:54:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加油"}]}